Dialogue: 0,0:00:-01.00,0:00:00.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inherited will...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.64,0:00:03.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The tide of the times...\NPeople's dreams...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.54,0:00:06.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These things cannot be stopped.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.38,0:00:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as people\Nseek the answer of freedom,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.48,0:00:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,these things will never cease to be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.03,0:00:27.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I only believe in the future --\NI don't care if anyone laughs
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.20,0:00:32.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That racing passion makes you shine
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.54,0:00:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's too bright,\Nbut I want to gaze at it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.54,0:00:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I sense "aesthetics" somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.15,0:00:45.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really really stuck on you
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.55,0:00:51.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I follow, follow in the footsteps\Nof a dream that resembles no one
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.99,0:00:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Until I dramatically get it
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.33,0:01:03.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.14,0:01:10.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to catch, catch the shape\Nof a dream no one can see
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:16.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to go with you,\Nso passionate feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't really\Nneed everything to add up
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.59,0:01:22.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than run-of-the-mill daily life,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.76,0:01:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,run for paradise instead
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.36,0:01:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Believe In Wonderland!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.30,0:01:39.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.01,0:01:44.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is a winter island!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.38,0:01:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The name of those mountains\Nis the Drum Rockies.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.31,0:01:51.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the castle on top of the\Ntallest mountain lives Dr. Kureha,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.58,0:01:57.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the only doctor in our country who is\Ncalled a "witch" by our country's people.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.39,0:02:00.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay then, Nami. Hang on tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.23,0:02:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.30,0:02:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch out for Lapins.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.08,0:02:19.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're carnivorous, ferocious bunnies.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.91,0:02:22.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you run into a group\Nof them, you're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.95,0:02:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have bodies like bears,\Nbut the agility of bunnies...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.19,0:02:32.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and they attack in groups.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.29,0:02:40.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.03,0:02:50.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're they doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.34,0:02:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those damn bunnies...\NThis can't be happening...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.18,0:02:56.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sanji. What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:58.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck is going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.78,0:03:04.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey... we're gonna run, Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.16,0:03:09.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Dalton's Resolve!\NWapol's Corps Lands On The Island"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.90,0:03:15.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,R-run? Where to?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.47,0:03:18.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't matter where! Someplace far!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.87,0:03:20.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.07,0:03:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An avalanche...! An avalanche is coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.58,0:03:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Those damn bunnies!\NThey'll never get away with this! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.02,0:03:35.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-wh-wh-what're we gonna do?!\NWh-wh-what're we gonna do, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.05,0:03:37.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How should I know?!\NThe first priority is Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.42,0:03:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The second is Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.09,0:03:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The third is Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.89,0:03:39.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fourth is Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.49,0:03:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the fifth is Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.79,0:03:42.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.26,0:03:44.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Protect her even if it kills you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.46,0:03:46.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.23,0:03:54.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But how?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.77,0:03:56.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! That cliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.78,0:03:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cliff?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.48,0:04:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run! We need to get as high up as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.08,0:04:10.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:23.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Good, we made... Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.10,0:04:31.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! We're not high enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.34,0:04:36.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol... Wapol came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.12,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.45,0:04:40.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san headed to Big Horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those who can fight, grab a\Nweapon and head to Big Horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.46,0:04:46.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry! Those who can fight,\Nhead to Big Horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.46,0:04:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.56,0:04:49.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Follow Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:51.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol came back!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.63,0:04:55.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone, grab a weapon!\NWe'll protect our country!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.13,0:04:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Grab a weapon! Head to Big Horn!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.54,0:05:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.98,0:05:05.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Vivi. Are you really sure\Nthis is the right direction
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.24,0:05:07.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to the Gyasta town where\Nthe witch is right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.11,0:05:10.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hmmm... When you put it that way,\NI'm not really sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.92,0:05:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're in trouble if you aren't sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.39,0:05:17.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, if Luffy and Sanji managed to get\Nto the castle and didn't find the doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.66,0:05:20.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,they'd think, "What're we doing?"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.66,0:05:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless we find the doctor soon and\Nask her to go back to the castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.20,0:05:26.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.67,0:05:30.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that, then do something.\NYou're a princess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.10,0:05:34.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That has nothing to do with this.\NI'm not a witch. I'm a princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.44,0:05:35.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.57,0:05:37.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you look at the map.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.98,0:05:42.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Don't be ridiculous!\NThere's snow everywhere. The map is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.15,0:05:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, you don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.08,0:05:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! I don't know at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have to be proud!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.92,0:05:53.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, there should be\Na sign for Gyasta on this route.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.29,0:05:54.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So don't miss it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.49,0:05:58.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Got it. Leave it to me!\NI'll watch for signs of the sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.80,0:06:06.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, ignoring me, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.74,0:06:13.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Delicious!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.95,0:06:20.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, citizens!\NEverything in this country is my snack!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.55,0:06:24.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm great! Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.12,0:06:27.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kuromarimo, tell them!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.06,0:06:31.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's because you're\Nthe king, Your Highness.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:34.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! That's exactly right!\NIf I wanna eat a house,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.57,0:06:36.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,there's nothing like one cooked\Nwell-done to a golden-brown after all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.80,0:06:38.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.34,0:06:40.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol-sama.\NI have some information for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.71,0:06:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:44.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I received a report that\Nsome of the Straw Hats
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.71,0:06:48.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,rudely headed towards Drum Castle.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.61,0:06:51.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.08,0:06:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems that they took a sick woman\Nto have her treated by a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.52,0:07:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such idiots! No one lives in my\Ncastle now, not to mention a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.93,0:07:05.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-well... I heard that\Nthe outrageous Dr. Kureha
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:10.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even more rudely currently\Nlives in Drum Castle...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.97,0:07:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! That old hag's\Nliving in my castle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.31,0:07:20.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just how much does she intend\Nto mock me?! Kick her out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Along with Straw Hat, I'll eat her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.78,0:07:26.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men, we're going back to the castle!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.18,0:07:29.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.02,0:07:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.03,0:07:37.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.00,0:07:41.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! I was cut down! I'm gonna die!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.53,0:07:42.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.80,0:07:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I came here to kill you.\NYou dying suits me just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.94,0:07:48.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard, Dalton!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.84,0:07:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you're alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.18,0:07:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you hurt Wapol-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.95,0:07:57.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It shouldn't be a big deal...\Nwith the excellent doctors of our country,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.25,0:08:00.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the "great medical care nation" Drum.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.85,0:08:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! The Twenty MDs\NExternal Injury Unit! Come forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.69,0:08:06.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.56,0:08:07.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:08.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.53,0:08:09.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.46,0:08:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.53,0:08:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.60,0:08:12.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Starting an operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.86,0:08:13.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Scalpel!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.40,0:08:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Needle!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.90,0:08:14.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.63,0:08:16.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.44,0:08:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I really thought I'd die!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.11,0:08:22.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like what happened now,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.47,0:08:25.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,you're the only one protected\Nand citizens have no choice
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.48,0:08:29.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but to suffer from sickness\Nwithout seeing doctors... Wapol!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.38,0:08:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol? It's Wapol-sama,\Nmy retainer Dalton.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.32,0:08:37.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's right! You don't\Nhave the right to blather!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:41.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The three of us, you included,\Nwere Wapol-sama's top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.86,0:08:45.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were his loyal hands, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.43,0:08:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that when you\Nwere making people suffer,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.20,0:08:50.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,all I could do was just watch
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.34,0:08:53.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,even though I was by your\Nside as one of your top brass.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.24,0:08:55.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to take responsibility for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.44,0:08:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol... Let's leave this country together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.64,0:09:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We must not stay in this land any longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.91,0:09:04.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san! You didn't do anything wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.82,0:09:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! You're the only one in the\Ngovernment who fought for the citizens!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.19,0:09:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even when it almost killed you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.52,0:09:14.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! You should've died...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,as the Captain of the\NDrum Kingdom's Security Guard!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.36,0:09:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm surprised that you survived in\Nthis country without any doctors.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.67,0:09:25.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Drum is acknowledged internationally\Nas a country with advanced medicine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.64,0:09:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But who would know... that there\Nwere actually only 20 doctors,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.87,0:09:33.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,who worked in the research\Nfacility of the King's castle,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.88,0:09:37.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and all the other doctors were exiled?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.65,0:09:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! Those who become\Nsick can beg for their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.32,0:09:47.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I feel like it, I might\Nlend them the Twenty MDs.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.39,0:09:52.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If they don't wanna die, all they\Nhave to do is obey me, the king!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.76,0:09:57.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With that, my ruling is perfect.\NThat's the government of this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.67,0:10:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't call that a government!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Humph! You sure speak\Nyour mind, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.51,0:10:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kill him! Kill your ex-captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.71,0:10:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As I figured, you don't\Nget what I'm saying...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.69,0:10:20.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're the son of the previous\Nking who was good to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.03,0:10:22.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I was hoping that you'd\Ncome to your senses some day,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but it seems like that\Nwas wishful thinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.36,0:10:26.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! There he goes! Ox Ox Fruit!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.70,0:10:29.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The model "Bison"!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.50,0:10:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't flinch! Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.77,0:10:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't hit him!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.94,0:10:36.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dodging them!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.91,0:10:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll show no mercy even though\Nyou're my ex-subordinates!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.08,0:10:50.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fiddle Bam!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's strong! How powerful!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.03,0:10:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So this is the wild power...\Nthe power of a Zoan type devil fruit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.93,0:11:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough with you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.63,0:11:03.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A country where the king\Nis the first to run off
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.94,0:11:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,when the country is in crisis\Nshould just die out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.04,0:11:10.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have a chance,\Nfighting against the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.14,0:11:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.11,0:11:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:15.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.91,0:11:17.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We've come to assist you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.28,0:11:18.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let us fight with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.75,0:11:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll protect this free country!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.86,0:11:30.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Above all, I've known you so long.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's unfortunate for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:33.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't...!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.47,0:11:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your weak point is...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.18,0:11:49.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.95,0:11:51.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...did you shield us...?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.28,0:11:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.25,0:11:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.86,0:11:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dalton-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.22,0:12:04.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's your weak point, kind Dalton-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.46,0:12:09.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a death befitting you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.87,0:12:11.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-what's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.44,0:12:16.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's going on? An earthquake?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.78,0:12:20.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, this isn't good. We can't go\Nfurther because of the deep snow.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.31,0:12:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like we went up the mountain...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.75,0:12:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.82,0:12:29.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's... this rumbling?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.92,0:12:33.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Usopp-san! Could this be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.53,0:12:37.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... A.. Avalanche...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.23,0:12:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25631... 25632... 25633...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.70,0:12:52.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm? What's going on? How noisy...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.81,0:13:03.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,25634...!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.30,0:13:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! We're not high enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.18,0:13:33.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.89,0:13:37.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.39,0:13:42.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji! Grab my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.76,0:13:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You saved my skin!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.43,0:13:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but... even though\Nwe won't sink in the snow,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.10,0:13:50.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,we'll go straight down the mountain\Nif we don't do anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.57,0:13:52.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.14,0:13:56.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hell no! We've come all\Nthis way and were almost
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.17,0:13:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,at the foot of that chimney mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.21,0:14:00.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We were just a step away from the doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.48,0:14:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Luffy! Come up with a way to stop this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:06.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Dammit, those damn hopping bunnies!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.55,0:14:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time I see them,\NI'll simmer them in a pot!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.12,0:14:18.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:24.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What're we gonna do, Sanji?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.17,0:14:27.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.44,0:14:39.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the heck's... with them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.55,0:14:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! Luffy! Look ahead! Ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.52,0:14:51.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! A rock! We're gonna crash!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.10,0:14:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't crash!\NYou're carrying Nami-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.84,0:15:10.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's easy to say, but...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.92,0:15:15.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're crashing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.99,0:15:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to treat ladies... gently!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.93,0:15:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.27,0:15:37.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.44,0:15:39.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh... That hit me good...! Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.54,0:15:47.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You idiot! Don't do stuff\Nlike that without telling me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.95,0:15:56.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhh! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.63,0:16:03.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh! It's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.30,0:16:04.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not stopping!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.87,0:16:06.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This village will be swallowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.44,0:16:10.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're getting out of here!\NChess! Kuromarimo! Get on!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.58,0:16:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robson!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.88,0:16:19.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robson, Serious Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.75,0:16:23.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wapol-sama! Please let us ride, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.25,0:16:27.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Get out of here on your own!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.96,0:16:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Robson! Hurry up! It's closing in on us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.73,0:16:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,W-w-w-w-w-w-w-w-w-w-we'll\Nbe fine! Don't worry, Vivi!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.60,0:16:42.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we get swallowed,\NI'll save you for sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.27,0:16:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, do you think\NLuffy-san and the others...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.65,0:16:51.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could they have been swallowed\Nby this avalanche?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.05,0:16:54.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhh! Wapol-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.19,0:16:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.52,0:16:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.92,0:16:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahh!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ahhhhh!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.82,0:18:10.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nami, are you cold?\NHang in there just a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.46,0:18:18.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen. Hold this. Stay here\Nand wait for me a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.91,0:18:55.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it was you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.84,0:18:58.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No wonder I thought\Nit was an awful syrup.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.98,0:19:00.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They'll never get away with this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.05,0:19:04.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot! Of course them!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.88,0:19:06.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Them meaning...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.65,0:19:08.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You said some Straw Hats
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.29,0:19:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,are going up the mountain\Nto the castle right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.32,0:19:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then this is what happened!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.39,0:19:17.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They have a huge grudge against\Nus over what happened between us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.43,0:19:22.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so they caused an avalanche\Non that snow mountain.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no! That's what happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.57,0:19:27.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, this avalanche was their doing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.81,0:19:30.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go! We'll follow\Nthem on the snow mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.51,0:19:38.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll teach them a lesson\Nabout battling in the snow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.30,0:21:03.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely get you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.33,0:21:06.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.37,0:21:13.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,both of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.48,0:21:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.25,0:21:17.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please look at that, Wapol-sama!\NWe found them!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.65,0:21:20.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.08,0:21:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you do\Nmany rude things to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.62,0:21:30.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll beat you up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.38,0:21:54.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even this sleepless town\Nhas dozed off for now
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.69,0:22:04.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,From today forth,\Nsomething's going to change
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.80,0:22:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure I can start fresh,\Nsince I'm not alone
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.08,0:22:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just by having you by my side,\NI feel I can become strong
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.55,0:22:36.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how far I can go,\Ntowards the place that leads to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.00,0:22:47.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Off in the distance it shines,\Nencompassing the world
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.31,0:22:55.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Before dawn
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.31,0:22:58.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Boy, that was close!\NI'm glad I'm still alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.88,0:23:01.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Suddenly hitting an avalanche in this cold...\NI must've run out of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.79,0:23:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But this is a sort of\Nwinter swimming, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.02,0:23:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What on earth is happening\Non the mountain?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.66,0:23:07.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if Luffy-san\Nand the others are okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.56,0:23:10.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will definitely get\Nyou there. Nami! Sanji!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.13,0:23:11.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So hang in there a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.76,0:23:13.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.10,0:23:15.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Island Where Snow Lives!\NClimb The Drum Rockies!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.97,0:23:23.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be King of the Pirates!!
